{"id":250452,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/09/维权网-上海维权人士到市政府声援被关黑监狱的/","date":"2012-09-06T17:31:17Z","modified":"2012-09-06T17:31:17Z","title":"维权网 | 上海维权人士到市政府声援被关黑监狱的朱金娣（组图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员晨晓报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日下午</span><span>，上海</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>位维权者到市政府声援被关黑监狱</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>天的上访维权人士朱金娣，维权者们打出“声援朱金娣砸烂黑监狱”、“</span><span> </span><span>砸烂黑监狱声援朱金娣”的标语，抗议地方政府随意限制公民的人身自由。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>上海访民朱金娣</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>日下午</span><span>在北京最高法院正常上访时，遭到上海浦东新区地方政府派遣到保安人员绑架。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日晚上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>时</span><span>多钟，朱金娣被押回上海，关押在地方政府私自设立的黑监狱内，此黑监狱是在上海市浦东大道</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2900</span><span>号金华旅馆</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">103</span><span>房间，至今朱金娣已被非法限制人身自由</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>朱金娣曾经打电话告诉朋友：自己被关押在上海市浦东大道</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2900</span><span>号金华（音同）旅馆</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">103</span><span>房间的黑监狱内，上海浦东新区沪东街道政府派</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6~7</span><span>个保安把守门口，不让她出房门一步。据看守人员讲，要到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>大会议开完才能放她回家。上海当局派沪东街道政法委书记王纪兵、信访综治科的韩俊到黑监狱，不但没有任何解决问题的诚意，还恐吓朱金娣：访民无论到北京或北戴河都是违法。因担心家中患忧郁症的儿子，朱金娣从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日</span><span>开始进行绝食裸体抗议。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日</span><span>朱金娣在黑监狱内绝食裸体抗议第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>天，她打电话告诉朋友，称自己已经打了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">168</span><span>个“</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>”</span><span>报警电话，无一出警。朋友在电话里听到有人猛烈敲房门和大声呼喊“快开门、快开门”的声音。此时，与朱金娣的通话中断，至今联系不上。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>多位上访维权者到朱金娣家里，向他儿子打听朱金娣到情况，她儿子说不知道。她儿子是忧郁症患者，不能正常饮食起居、不能打理家务，且无人照顾他。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>朱金娣儿子的商铺在上海浦东陆家嘴，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span><span>年被强拆。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2009</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月份在中共建国六十周年之际，朱金娣因关注侵权个案被上海市公安局浦东新区分局刑拘</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日。朱金娣期满释放回家发现儿子目光痴呆、自言自语。朱金娣多次带儿子求医，都诊断为忧郁症。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>朱金娣多次找有关领导反映其儿子在陆家嘴的商铺遭强拆后久拖不决的问题，造成自己的儿子得了忧郁症。有关领导居然称“不是忧郁症，是对社会不满”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>朱金娣</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2002</span><span>年私房拆迁安置中遭到法院枉法裁判而上访。在上访维权及关注其他访民的过程中，曾遭到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>次刑拘，多次被关黑监狱。由于上访受到监控、关押等迫害，她儿子忧郁症的病越来越严重。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>位上海维权者（签名单详见附图）请求媒体和社会各界正义人士关注朱金娣和她儿子的处境。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-BAQYVyDllDM/UEjKJBBqB7I/AAAAAAAANeI/Sk_IAP0bK68/s1600/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E7%BB%B4%E6%9D%83%E8%80%85%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%97%E8%AE%AE%EF%BC%9A%E2%80%9C%E7%A0%B8%E7%83%82%E9%BB%91%E7%9B%91%E7%8B%B1%E5%A3%B0%E6%8F%B4%E6%9C%B1%E9%87%91%E5%A8%A3%E2%80%9D.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"205\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-BAQYVyDllDM/UEjKJBBqB7I/AAAAAAAANeI/Sk_IAP0bK68/s320/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E7%BB%B4%E6%9D%83%E8%80%85%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%97%E8%AE%AE%EF%BC%9A%E2%80%9C%E7%A0%B8%E7%83%82%E9%BB%91%E7%9B%91%E7%8B%B1%E5%A3%B0%E6%8F%B4%E6%9C%B1%E9%87%91%E5%A8%A3%E2%80%9D.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>上海维权者在市政府门前拉横幅：“声援朱金娣砸烂黑监狱”</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-NHCxP5lBKlg/UEjKQoQvogI/AAAAAAAANeQ/OXcVk4krWIA/s1600/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E7%BB%B4%E6%9D%83%E8%80%85%E5%9C%A8%E5%B8%82%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%97%A8%E5%89%8D%E6%8B%89%E6%A8%AA%E5%B9%85%EF%BC%9A%E2%80%9C%E5%A3%B0%E6%8F%B4%E6%9C%B1%E9%87%91%E5%A8%A3%E7%A0%B8%E7%83%82%E9%BB%91%E7%9B%91%E7%8B%B1%E2%80%9D.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"211\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-NHCxP5lBKlg/UEjKQoQvogI/AAAAAAAANeQ/OXcVk4krWIA/s320/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E7%BB%B4%E6%9D%83%E8%80%85%E5%9C%A8%E5%B8%82%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%97%A8%E5%89%8D%E6%8B%89%E6%A8%AA%E5%B9%85%EF%BC%9A%E2%80%9C%E5%A3%B0%E6%8F%B4%E6%9C%B1%E9%87%91%E5%A8%A3%E7%A0%B8%E7%83%82%E9%BB%91%E7%9B%91%E7%8B%B1%E2%80%9D.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-wqqVoAif-7Q/UEjKWl3xMuI/AAAAAAAANeY/M7wJloZX1yE/s1600/%E5%A3%B0%E6%8F%B4%E6%9C%B1%E9%87%91%E5%A8%A3%E7%AD%BE%E5%90%8D%E5%8D%95.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-wqqVoAif-7Q/UEjKWl3xMuI/AAAAAAAANeY/M7wJloZX1yE/s320/%E5%A3%B0%E6%8F%B4%E6%9C%B1%E9%87%91%E5%A8%A3%E7%AD%BE%E5%90%8D%E5%8D%95.jpg\" width=\"228\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-3336747646811104339?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories